Meet the Authess™ Team
Chris KaiserCo-FounderBiology Professor and former provost at MIT. Dedicated teacher and education thought leader.  


Paul Crockett CEO & Co-FounderIndustry veteran with focus on innovation, strategy, and product management, including next-gen strategy.  
  


Sundar Subramaniam Co-FounderCompany builder and proven leader of lean, execution-oriented teams.    



Ali Mohammad VP of Artificial IntelligenceFocused on AI engine and backend architecture. Sc.D. in computer science from MIT. Principal engineer at Google and edX.   



Steve Stalzer VP of EngineeringLeads development, guides architecture and design. Senior engineering leader with gaming, mobile, and big data industry experience.



David Martz VP of Business DevelopmentLeads disciplined sales and consulting process to secure and sustain happy customers. Industry Veteran, leveraging innovative technologies for education and training. 



Anna Shults Senior Project & Client ManagerManages projects from contract to delivery and delights customers.   



Mark Luetzelschwab Product & Market Development AdvisorInforms development based on track record of award-winning education technology products.



Yigal Rosen Assessment and Learning Design AdvisorInforms creation of innovative, evidence-based authentic assessment solutions.


